underlying_goal: To check if a provided paper-critique rubric is already part of the existing tooling.
primary_success: Correctly identifying that the user's provided rubric already existed verbatim within a file referenced by an existing /review-paper skill.
brief_summary: The user provided a detailed rubric for reviewing papers and asked if it was already part of the system. Claude correctly identified that the exact rubric was already used by the /review-paper skill, explained the existing tooling, and prevented redundant effort.
